{"tid":415936,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 行山出事應唔應該報警？","createTime":"2017-09-27T11:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T21:25:02.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fde1d07bb5b997f100f86763da7f8e601e1467d6","tid":415936,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=891841340965059&amp;id=481487895333741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D891841340965059%26id%3D481487895333741&d=t1bT9n%2B3oRbgiqcc%2BMDm6gIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=e116e271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=891841340965059&amp;id=481487895333741</a><br />\n<br />\n自從上次吊手岩死咗個消防員之後，發現次次一有人行山出事，無論消防員有冇傷都好，成班道德撚就狂屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如早兩日有行山人士迷路報警，到第二朝先落返山，冇人有事不過都俾人公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純討論，如果有人行山出事，例如迷路或者受傷，應唔應該報警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2578ddae04df9d7ebade4e4157053e59bab2cb29","tid":415936,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1984c881eb20090f89eae45cbdd78f43a16dc6a9","tid":415936,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"唔應該行山"},{"pid":"a71a681220ba8ef61251f0b6cfcbd6343b8f3289","tid":415936,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔係斷手斷腳，即時生命危險都冇咩必要報警"},{"pid":"442d83961f08981b3b0437b04e92aa660fa8713a","tid":415936,"uid":9805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實點都要報,因為即使你死左,都有人要上山搵你條屍,而且你可能已經好臭,又脹曬,到時直係多得你唔少,風險同救你差唔多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最撚緊要係咪撚on99咁行埋啲非常規路線,咪撚信堆on9港女行山page<br />\n仲有打風落雨咪撚行山</span></span><br />\n唔係既話係香港其實你帶夠水其實好難出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7b01ef8baba2c5e712484193a1810dfbffa892","tid":415936,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54ab711e1a78c32fe1ecef352d7702bd1f933f9","tid":415936,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9325ad5b000910d23fbb3c682e36ffa99eb8670e","tid":415936,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"on9, 出事緊係報警啦，比連登仔屌兩下又唔會少忽肉，過一個禮拜就無人記得件事啦"},{"pid":"7a1ccd38f45fa703aed0d4a658e0c5c2b11b55da","tid":415936,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T19:55:04.000Z","msg":"真係出事梗係報<br />\n你死咗咪又係要搵人搵你<br />\n不過唔識行就咪撚亂鳩咁行"},{"pid":"5ce004b0d731231b8917d057852fa5f5823927ad","tid":415936,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T21:25:02.000Z","msg":"你都唔撚明重點"}]}